				<wikidot:authorName>Lesh</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1432306</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Pictographs within the vehicle, as well as limited translation of the organisms' language, suggests they originate from Saturn's moon Titan.</p> </blockquote> <p>I like how this implies the Foundation is already fully aware of a Titanian language. The lack of further information makes it seem that this is relatively mundane for Foundation researchers.</p> <p>The article gives me a series I vibe, and in a good way!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
